      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Herkes ayn\u0131 kelimeyi \xF6\u011Frenir.\n\nAma i\xE7imizden biri Imposter
    olur. Ona verilen kelime daha geneldir ve yan\u0131nda \u201CImposter\u201D yazar.\n\nHerkes
    s\u0131rayla kelimeyle ilgili ipu\xE7lar\u0131 verir.\n\nGer\xE7ek oyuncular
    ayn\u0131 kelimeyi bildi\u011Fi i\xE7in ipu\xE7lar\u0131 birbirine benzer.\n\nImposter
    farkl\u0131 kelimeyi bildi\u011Fi i\xE7in bazen \u015Fa\u015F\u0131r\u0131r!\n\nG\xF6revimiz:\n\nOyuncular:
    \u0130pu\xE7lar\u0131ndan Imposter\u2019\u0131 bulmaya \xE7al\u0131\u015F\u0131r.\n\nImposter:
    Yakalanmadan aram\u0131za kar\u0131\u015Fmaya \xE7al\u0131\u015F\u0131r!\n\nEn
    sonunda oylama yap\u0131l\u0131r ve en \u015F\xFCpheli ki\u015Fi se\xE7ilir. "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 22d200ea5dc82934fa69dacfad738fa2, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 8913695872570179388, guid: 22d200ea5dc82934fa69dacfad738fa2, type: 2}
